-- Turkey's Garanti Bank secures $550 million, 20-year financing
-- By Ece Toksabay
-- Thu Apr 24, 2014 03:18AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, April 24 (Reuters) - Turkey's Garanti Bank <GARAN.IS> said on Thursday it secured $550 million in financing with a maturity of 20 years through a "future flow" transaction.

